Wait a minute. No, no! I'm good.

1818
01:18:31,607 --> 01:18:34,310
My family jewels!

1819
01:18:34,310 --> 01:18:35,578
[JAKE]
Damn eye patch!

1820
01:18:35,578 --> 01:18:36,545
Jake!

1821
01:18:36,545 --> 01:18:38,147
I was aimin' for his knees!

1822
01:18:38,147 --> 01:18:40,950
[WARD whimpering]

1823
01:18:40,950 --> 01:18:42,885
He went down like a stag!

1824
01:18:42,885 --> 01:18:45,087
[TALLY] How'd you, uh...
How'd you find us?

1825
01:18:45,087 --> 01:18:47,256
Oh! I had one more message
from your old man.

1826
01:18:47,256 --> 01:18:48,123
After you found the cabin,

1827
01:18:48,123 --> 01:18:51,427
1 figured you boys
might get lost. And...

1828
01:18:51,427 --> 01:18:52,828
Heard the shootin'
and I thought:

1829
01:18:52,828 --> 01:18:55,331
Good God, maybe they've gone
to killin' each other!

1830
01:18:55,331 --> 01:18:57,099
[WARD cries]

1831
01:18:57,099 --> 01:18:58,901
Play it, yeah.

1832
01:18:58,901 --> 01:19:00,803
--Shut up! Stop whinin'.
--[thuds]

1833
01:19:00,803 --> 01:19:05,407
[WARD]
ow! Ow... Ow...

1834
01:19:05,407 --> 01:19:08,611
All right, no jokes this time.

1835
01:19:08,611 --> 01:19:10,012
I know our family's
been a little,

1836
01:19:10,012 --> 01:19:12,514
well... dysfunctional.

1837
01:19:12,514 --> 01:19:14,283
But what family isn't?

1838
01:19:14,283 --> 01:19:16,485
By now you know the cabin
and what money I had left

1839
01:19:16,485 --> 01:19:17,786
is yours to split between you.

1840
01:19:17,786 --> 01:19:19,989
But what you may not know

1841
01:19:19,989 --> 01:19:22,191
is I didn't just rebuild
Elmer's ranch for him--

1842
01:19:22,191 --> 01:19:23,626
I bought it.

1843
01:19:23,626 --> 01:19:26,128
He's been my business
partner ever since.

1844
01:19:26,128 --> 01:19:29,632
It's my hope that you boys
will continue on with it.

1845
01:19:29,632 --> 01:19:30,666
But hell, you're grown men,

1846
01:19:30,666 --> 01:19:32,534
you can do whatever
the hell you like.

1847
01:19:32,534 --> 01:19:36,472
[sighs] I'm real proud
of you boys.

1848
01:19:36,472 --> 01:19:37,773
Truth is, I always have been,

1849
01:19:37,773 --> 01:19:39,475
I just didn't know
how to show it.

1850
01:19:39,475 --> 01:19:42,278
All the money and fame in
the world is not worth a dime

1851
01:19:42,278 --> 01:19:46,181
if you don't have people
to love and share it with.

1852
01:19:46,181 --> 01:19:48,784
Sol leave you with
this one last thought.

1853
01:19:48,784 --> 01:19:51,654
It's very simple, just like me.

1854
01:19:51,654 --> 01:19:53,822
love you boys...

1855
01:19:53,822 --> 01:19:57,660
1 always have
and I always will.

1856
01:19:57,660 --> 01:19:58,827
You might not realize it now,

1857
01:19:58,827 --> 01:20:03,465
but you are gonna miss
me when I'm gone...

1858
01:20:03,465 --> 01:20:04,533
Now go on out there,

1859
01:20:04,533 --> 01:20:06,635
