1887
01:21:20,476 --> 01:21:21,377
[MAV]
I got you.

1888
01:21:21,377 --> 01:21:23,879
[TALLY]
Punch him. Somebody needs to.

1889
01:21:23,879 --> 01:21:26,871
Okay. I'll be
over therein asec.

1890
